						<summary>

						<p>On a stone slab set up in a field.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">M.K. Parakēsarivarman (Parāntaka I) Year 29: 936 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records that when cattle were lifted at Mukkuṭṭūr by Perumānaḍigaḷ, Vadunavāraṉ Varadaṉ Tāṇḍaṉ recovered the cattle but died.</p>						

						<p>Published in <hi rend="italic">Ep. Ind.,</hi> Vol. IV. p. 179.</p>						

						</summary>
